5 b. A local school board member or their spouse.[.]
6 (2) Each local board of education shall adopt a policy for implementing school-based
7 policies[decision making] in the district which shall include but not be limited to a
8 description of how the district's policies, including those developed pursuant to
9 KRS 160.340, have been amended to allow the professional staff members of a
