8 (c) 1. High-quality, evidence-based suicide prevention training, including risk
9 factors, warning signs, protective factors, response procedures, referral,
10 postvention, and the recognition of signs and symptoms of possible
11 mental illness.
12 2. As used in this paragraph, "postvention" means a series of planned
