14 purpose of facilitating the grieving or adjustment process, stabilizing the
15 environment, reducing the risk of negative behaviors, and limiting the
16 risk of further suicides through contagion; and
17 (d) Self-study review of seizure disorder materials.
18 (3) (a) Each local school district superintendent shall appoint a certified school
