17 test items that require the student to create an answer rather than select a
18 response and may include fill-in-the-blank, short-answer, extended-answer,
19 open-response, and writing-on-demand formats;
20 (d) "Criterion-referenced test" means a test that is aligned with defined academic
21 content standards and measures an individual student's level of performance
22 against the standards;
23 (e) "Formative assessment" means a process used by teachers and students during
24 instruction to adjust ongoing teaching and learning to improve students'
