21 progress through the relevant curricula and complete each assessment level
22 required by the Kentucky Board of Education for the state assessment
23 program established under KRS 158.6453 and in compliance with the
24 requirements of the federal Every Student Succeeds Act of 2015, Pub. L. No.
25 114-95, or its successor; and
